Package transaction

Class Transaction

java.lang.Object
transaction.Transaction
public class Transaction extends Object
The Transaction class represents a transaction associated with bike rental. It contains information about the customer, rental details, status, and transaction type.

    • Transaction

      public Transaction(Integer transactionId, Customer customer, Timestamp createdAt, Long deposit, Bike bike, String status, String transactionType, Integer minuteUsed, Timestamp lastPause)
      Constructs a new Transaction instance with the given details.
      Parameters:
      transactionId - The unique identifier for the transaction.
      customer - The customer associated with the transaction.
      createdAt - The timestamp indicating when the transaction was created.
      deposit - The deposit amount for the transaction.
      bike - The bike associated with the transaction.
      status - The status of the transaction (e.g., ongoing, completed, paused).
      transactionType - The type of the transaction (e.g., rental, return).
      minuteUsed - The number of minutes the bike was used in the transaction.
      lastPause - The timestamp indicating when the transaction was last paused (if applicable).
